INCIPIT grimoire "codegen_gate_ordo_payload_basic_27c_input"

ORDO Option
  None
  Some(value: REX)
FIN ORDO

RITUALE make(REX value) REDDE Option
  REDDE Some(value)
EXPLICIT RITUALE

RITUALE main() REDDE REX
  EVOCA Option opt AD make(7)
  EVOCA Option copy AD opt
  VINCIRE opt AD copy
  REDDE 5
EXPLICIT RITUALE

EXPLICIT grimoire
